:05.000Z","msg":"集中火力全面升級科技先有得贏。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WQqvcqTbUKc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWQqvcqTbUKc&d=DwP82Rd5Y8BeeioconDBYQ8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=7cea6f60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WQqvcqTbUKc</a><br />\n<br />\n製作酒精大砲！我們終於演進至火器時代啦！【胡思亂搞】<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uyiZcry4RaA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DuyiZcry4RaA&d=DwP82Rd5Y8BeeioconDBYQ8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=9f0f72da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uyiZcry4RaA</a><br />\n<br />\nPVC複合弓！這下子就算殭屍末日來襲我也不用怕啦！【胡思亂搞】(Feat.末日希望)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7NW44DTHUhM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7NW44DTHUhM&d=DwP82Rd5Y8BeeioconDBYQ8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=dc068db4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7NW44DTHUhM</a><br />\n<br />\n自製可以防禦實彈的盾牌？竹子的用途真的超乎想像欸！【胡思亂搞】<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8RmIm9mkUvI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8RmIm9mkUvI&d=DwP82Rd5Y8BeeioconDBYQ8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=732878d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8RmIm9mkUvI</a>"},{"pid":"0d6f778c4010f50b7a17b4e9046b26d4ae8cec75","tid":1723081,"uid":40118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"656d115f60e4085cac7691c2c45d31d74fc3c356","tid":1723081,"uid":101606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T05:36:15.000Z","msg":"一個種票既遊戲有咩意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:25:50.000Z","msg":"唔好單純地黑與白咁話有定無用。過去種要咁嚴重泛民都贏到百幾席。好多區帝制派只贏5%-10%， 今時今日民意隨時翻盤。<br />\n<br />\n而我相信今屆既種票係難左，因為轉地址而家要地址證明，要種票難以登記一個三唔識七既地址搏大霧。<br />\n<br />\n要知道一個議席只計薪金津貼涉及幾百萬公帑。要瓦解帝制派既動員，拆走呢d錢係好重要。"},{"pid":"66d8d6edf48ebe687a4600aa98e998631140bdd2","tid":1723081,"uid":193476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:25:52.000Z","msg":"區議會同立法無直接關係，又一直被控制，所以好多人覺得唔重要<br />\n但係區議會係一個政府＞建制＞鄉紳/黑社會既合作方式<br />\n黑社會係可以透過區議會獲得資金，成日有啲奇怪工程，什麼青年會，慶祝乜乜乜，政府係咁樣去派錢比佢地<br />\n<br />\n如果你覺得裝修需要做，用制度去停止黑社會資金來源更加重要，所以點解成日有人吹要停區選，要記住黑社會係認錢唔認人，假如維穩費派唔到比一班鄉紳黑社會，佢地一樣同會呢個政府反面"},{"pid":"4cf51f13790aeb334d3f8a7ae4673b7b2f2e2253","tid":1723081,"uid":40118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26159a6bb29dc2bfaa7d516c8f902b3582eb3cb9","tid":1723081,"uid":101606,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T05:42:07.000Z","msg":"唔係支持法外抗爭？點解要跟人地規矩玩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:26:23.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山"},{"pid":"b0ecac01e3edad0bf79d44493a2a772d2d5e49e5","tid":1723081,"uid":34553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:28:01.000Z","msg":"唔好再問<br />\n而家係咩陣線都要贏<br />\n咩資源都要拎"},{"pid":"99b4acb7716a2795a18b6503e4572ee517320dec","tid":1723081,"uid":274722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:29:17.000Z","msg":"因為popo今時今日仲係冇穿冇爛，對家冇明顯懲罰"},{"pid":"6146da59b50acb42a73898f6095ae0be74b16e0a","tid":1723081,"uid":281020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e584caf573e9bbf63abf24dd15873efffa44ca3","tid":1723081,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b686bb2d82ea0b0cfaa2262f8a4d7a38dc871c7","tid":1723081,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"68634aa0f5b6823e0a5e7e59bbab04b4c0107361","tid":1723081,"uid":101606,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T05:40:20.000Z","msg":"認真問 如果最後輸左係咪代表民意不支持五大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:20:14.000Z","msg":"佢哋扮睇唔到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:21:58.000Z","msg":"點為之輸咗，唔過半？<br />\n區選唔係單一議題<br />\n參選人往績、地區工作表現影響好大<br />\n當然唔算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:30:10.000Z","msg":"03年區議會已經話咗比你聽<br />\n區議會唔係絕對剩係講地區工作<br />\n剩係靠政治議題都可以嬴<br />\n區選當然唔係單一議題<br />\n但係依個時勢 任你點解讀<br />\n今次依個選舉一定係對革命支持或反對既投票"},{"pid":"a89f2223101042175f746eb11d38be1002ad3bf9","tid":1723081,"uid":56714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68634aa0f5b6823e0a5e7e59bbab04b4c0107361","tid":1723081,"uid":101606,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T05:40:20.000Z","msg":"認真問 如果最後輸左係咪代表民意不支持五大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:30:21.000Z","msg":"非建制過半數 = WIN<br />\n建制過半數 = 種票<br />\n<br />\n你真係唔識嫁喎"},{"pid":"9f353652a6179a86deef1589b1981f587d1f79d2","tid":1723081,"uid":101756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T06:34:09.000Z","msg":"."}]}